{"tid":1532962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太子站一事 我有意見！","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:12:23.000Z","uid":208257,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"683d646750835c59c95a0afa342e39686416bd7e","tid":1532962,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"其實太子站一事<br />\n我個人意見<br />\n而家班狗封吃個站兩日<br />\n一定仲處理緊啲證據同毁屍波威跡<br />\n但佢地絕對係守果方<br />\n全香港咁多人你要圍佢嘅話要攻一個地下<br />\n地鐵站唔會攻唔入<br />\n依家黑警殺人毀屍滅跡但係大家就冇好好把握機會事件發生之後最黃金嘅時間<br />\n一但攻左入去成件事嘅真相所有證據就會係國際社會曝光點解完全有人說過要咁樣做？係咪要手足白白犧牲？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知道大家意見如何</span></strong>"},{"pid":"634d86ba8772fe6b45b336b93d34af0663d9fda7","tid":1532962,"uid":132497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"45184855fdcf6aa53e43f74e8cabf9dc3cc56482","tid":1532962,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e84e4d53f3e61c5cb9ebd14d90bd30812a69ceb","tid":1532962,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:27